Well, thank you all so much for joining us.

00:54:55.439 --> 00:54:59.280
It's really awesome to hear how well the data jam went

00:54:59.280 --> 00:55:01.439
and how many people were interested in the event too.

00:55:02.080 --> 00:55:04.159
There's been a number of people who've reached out to me

00:55:04.159 --> 00:55:07.439
around holding their own sort of data competitions.

00:55:07.439 --> 00:55:11.439
And I'm so excited to be able to share this as a resource with them too.

00:55:11.439 --> 00:55:12.879
Thank you so much for having us.

00:55:12.879 --> 00:55:13.439
This was fun.

00:55:13.439 --> 00:55:14.159
Thanks Rachel.

